# Component Patterns

## File Organization

```
src/components/
  layout/          # Shell components (LeftNav, TopNav, etc.)
  ui/              # Reusable primitives (Button, Input, etc.)
  features/        # Feature-specific components
```

## Imports Order

1. React/external libraries
2. Lucide icons
3. Internal utilities (`cn`, etc.)
4. Assets (images, SVGs)
5. Local components/types

## Styling Conventions

- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Use `cn()` helper for conditional classes
- Avoid inline styles except for dynamic values or SVG gradients

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
className={cn(
  'base-classes here',
  condition && 'conditional-class'
)}

// ❌ BAD
style={{ padding: '16px' }}
```

## Button Patterns

```tsx
// Icon button (nav actions)
<button
  type="button"
  className="flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-brand-navy transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-100"
>
  <Icon size={16} />
</button>
```

## Nav Item Pattern

```tsx
// With tooltip
<div className="group relative" title={label}>
  <span className="pointer-events-none absolute left-full ml-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md bg-brand-navy px-2 py-1 text-xs text-white opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100">
    {label}
  </span>
  {/* Button content */}
</div>
```

## SVG Gradient Icons

For animated AI icons, use inline SVG with `gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"`:

```tsx
<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="uniqueId" x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="21" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
      <stop className="animate-class" stopColor="#1c1b2e" />
      <stop className="animate-class" offset="1" stopColor="#1c1b2e" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <path stroke="url(#uniqueId)" ... />
</svg>
```

## TrapezoidalTabs Component

Custom tab component with trapezoidal SVG shapes:

```tsx
import { TrapezoidalTabs, type TabItem } from "@/components/ui/TrapezoidalTabs";

const TABS: TabItem[] = [
  { id: "tab-1", label: "Tab 1" },
  { id: "tab-2", label: "Tab 2" },
];

<TrapezoidalTabs
  tabs={TABS}
  activeTab={activeTab}
  onTabChange={setActiveTab}
  compact={isCompact}  // Optional: smaller height on scroll
/>
```

## Data Table Pattern

Clean, minimal tables with horizontal scroll support:

```tsx
<div className="overflow-x-auto border-t border-neutral-200">
  <table className="w-full min-w-[800px]">
    <thead>
      <tr className="border-b border-neutral-200">
        <th className="py-2 pr-4 text-left text-[11px] font-normal uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-fog">
          Column
        </th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr className="border-b border-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-50 cursor-pointer transition-colors">
        <td className="py-2.5 pr-4 text-[14px] text-brand-navy">
          Content
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

## Filter Tag Pattern (Notion-style)

```tsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-2.5">
  {/* Icon button - no border */}
  <button className="text-brand-navy hover:text-brand-fog transition-colors">
    <Search size={14} />
  </button>
  
  {/* Filter pill with label */}
