## Compact Tag Pattern

For status/type indicators in tables:

```tsx
// Grey neutral tag (task types)
<span className="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2 py-0.5 text-[12px] font-medium whitespace-nowrap bg-neutral-100 text-brand-navy border-neutral-200">
  Label
</span>

// Colored tag (severity)
<span className="inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-[12px] font-medium whitespace-nowrap bg-red-50 text-red-600">
  Critical
</span>
```

## Full-Page Modal Pattern

Almost-full-page modals with 16px padding, 24px rounded corners, transparent black overlay:

```tsx
// Outer wrapper with overlay
<div className="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex p-4">
  {/* Backdrop - clickable to close */}
  <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40" onClick={onClose} />
  
  {/* Modal panel */}
  <div className="relative z-10 flex h-full w-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] bg-white">
    {/* Top bar with close, title, CTA */}
    <div className="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 px-6 py-4">
      <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
        <button type="button" onClick={onClose} className="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-brand-fog hover:bg-neutral-100">
          <X size={20} />
        </button>
        <h1 className="font-heading text-[18px] font-semibold text-brand-navy">Title</h1>
      </div>
      <button className="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-violet-500 px-5 py-2.5 font-heading text-[14px] font-semibold text-white">
        CTA <ArrowRight size={16} />
      </button>
    </div>
    
    {/* Body - two column layout */}
    <div className="grid min-h-0 flex-1 grid-cols-2 gap-4 p-4">
      <div className="min-h-0 overflow-hidden">{/* Left content */}</div>
      <div className="min-h-0 overflow-y-auto">{/* Right content */}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Inline Edit Field Pattern

Click-to-edit fields that show as text, become editable inputs on click:

```tsx
import { InlineEditField, InlineEditSelect, InlineEditCheckbox, InlineEditRadioGroup } from '@/components/ui/InlineEditField'

// Text input - click to edit
<InlineEditField
  label="Email ID"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  required
  type="email"
  helperText="Optional helper text below"
/>

// Select dropdown
<InlineEditSelect
  label="Language"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  options={[{ value: 'en', label: 'English' }]}
/>

// Checkbox with helper
<InlineEditCheckbox
  label="Do not sync"
  checked={checked}
  onChange={setChecked}
  helperText="Check to disable syncing"
/>

// Radio group
<InlineEditRadioGroup
  label="Auto-collection"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  options={[{ value: 'on', label: 'ON' }, { value: 'off', label: 'OFF' }]}
/>
```

