## Segmented Toggle Pattern

Two-option toggle buttons (e.g., Link to existing / Create new):

```tsx
<div className="flex">
  <button
    className={cn(
      'flex items-center gap-2 rounded-l-lg border px-4 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium transition-colors',
      isActive
        ? 'border-violet-500 bg-violet-500 text-white'
        : 'border-neutral-200 bg-white text-brand-navy hover:bg-neutral-50'
    )}
  >
    <Link2 size={14} />
    Link to existing
  </button>
  <button
    className={cn(
      'flex items-center gap-2 rounded-r-lg border-y border-r px-4 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium transition-colors',
      !isActive
        ? 'border-violet-500 bg-violet-500 text-white'
        : 'border-neutral-200 bg-white text-brand-navy hover:bg-neutral-50'
    )}
  >
    <Sparkles size={14} />
    Create new customer
  </button>
</div>
```

## Form Section Card Pattern

Grouped form fields in rounded cards:

```tsx
<section className="rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5">
  <h3 className="mb-4 text-[15px] font-semibold text-brand-navy">Section Title</h3>
  <div className="space-y-4">
    {/* Form fields */}
  </div>
