```

## Extracted/Mapped Row Pattern

Show source data mapped to target with arrow indicator:

```tsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-4">
  {/* Source card */}
  <div className="flex-1 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-4">
    {/* Content */}
  </div>
  
  {/* Arrow */}
  <ArrowRight size={20} className="shrink-0 text-brand-mist" />
  
  {/* Target box - empty state */}
  <div className="flex-1 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <Building2 size={24} className="text-neutral-300" />
      <p className="text-[12px] text-brand-mist">Mapped to</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  {/* Target box - filled state */}
  <div className="flex-1 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-300 bg-green-50 p-4">
    {/* Mapped customer content */}
  </div>
</div>
```
